BAFTA award-winning Numberblocks helps children to see how numbers really work ‚àí and master a new key maths skill with every adventure.

recommended_videos.description:
Millie summons the Gremmies to fix her scooter but ends up receiving a number of unwanted upgrades for their tent. The problem is that the Gremmies are not very good at planning, leaving the fate of the tent up in the air.

---

Deep in the forest lives a friendly, fearless young girl called Millie and her best friend Lou, a clever and cautious little cat. Millie and Lou, however, do not live in the forest alone‚Ä¶ they share it with exciting creates called Forest Folk which are all based on mythical folklore.

Together, these best friends are embarking on a mission to meet every single one member of the Forest Folkies. 

This enchanting animated preschool series enhances the magic of making new friends and finding common ground, regardless of who you are and where you come from which is a sentiment we at Blue Zoo are keen to emphasise. 

Created by the talented Mandy Wong and Rory Cooke and produced by Blue Zoo Animation, we are incredibly proud and excited to introduce you to Millie and Lou.

For more Millie and Lou fun, visit www.millieandlou.com!
